attributes.action: For  our Labour government to press Dentists to treat NHS patients ASAP
attributes.additional_details: The government must ask before it is too late if the government can arrange for ILLEGAL  IMIGRANTS to be treated they can arrange for us the public to be treated
attributes.background: We must press the government to act allowing Dentists to treat NHS patients ASAP people are pulling their own teeth out / people are in agony as they cannot get into a Dentist

rejection.details:
You may wish to sign these petitions, which call for similar action: 

"Increase funding for NHS dentists and the NHS dentistry system" https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/743481

"Provide funding to put an NHS dentist in all GP surgeries" 
https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/725892
